text: Sunday Service for English Service is every Sunday 830am to 10am.

We are staying for 2 nights in Singapore. I and my son lost a way back to our hotel and phone battery was flat. We stopped in front of this church and asked for a direction. There were a group of people who were willing to assist us. One of them let the others go first and was kindly waiting for us to catch a taxi. Couldn’t ask his name but we could feel that he was such a gentleman. We wish to say “thank you” again. Thank you.
Too many lights in the main hall - 140 of them??
I go there every week and it's awesome
I am the member of that church but I must worship through zoom due to the covid-19
